<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/home.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
  <title>Document</title>
</head>

<body>
  <header>
    <div class="nav-bar">
      <div class="logo">LOGO</div>
      
      <ul class="nav-options">
        <li class="nav-option">
          <a href="home">Home</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-option switch">
          <a href="#">Switch Account</a>
          <div class="switch-box">
            <div class="round"></div>
            <ul class="switch-options">
              <li class="switch-option">
                <a href="sell">want to sell</a>
              </li>
              <div class="line"></div>
              <li class="switch-option">
                <a href="buy">want to buy</a>
              </li>
              <div class="line"></div>
              <li class="switch-option">
                <a href="#">want to deliver</a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-option">
          <a href="about_us">About Us</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-option">
          <a href="contact_us">Contact Us</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-option login_create" onclick="openLoginForm" >
          <a href="#">Login / Sign in</a>
        </li> 
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="login-background">
      <div class="login-form">
        <p1>Login</p1>
        <div class="line"></div>
        <div class="form">
          <form action="/login" method="POST">
            <div class="input-text">
              <label for="email-id-login">YOUR EMAIL-ID*</label>
              <input type="text" id="email-id-login" name="email" required>
            </div>
            <div class="input-text">
              <label for="password-login">PASSWORD*</label>
              <input type="password" id="password-login" name="password" required>
            </div>
            <input class="submit-button" type="submit" value="Login">
            <div class="sign-in-link">new here? please sign in</div>
          </form>
          <div class="login-cross" data-form="login"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="create-background">
      <div class="create-form">
        <p1>Create Account</p1>
        <div class="line"></div>
        <div class="form">
          <form action="/register" method="POST">
            <div class="input-text">
              <label for="name">YOUR NAME*</label>
              <div class="full-text">
                <input class="first" type="text" id="first-name" name="first_name" placeholder="First name" required>
                <input class="last" type="text" id="last-name" name="last_name" placeholder="Last name" required>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="input-text">
              <label for="email-id-create">YOUR EMAIL-ID*</label>
              <input class="input-text" type="email" id="email-id-create" name="email" placeholder="Eg. example@gmail.com" required>
            </div>
            <div class="input-text">
              <label for="number">MOBILE NUMBER*</label>
              <input class="input-text" type="text" id="number" name="phone" value="+91" minlength="13" maxlength="13" pattern="+,[0-9]" placeholder="Eg. +911234567890" required>
            </div>
            <div class="input-text">
              <label for="password-create">PASSWORD*</label>
              <input class="input-text" type="password" id="password-create" name="password" required>
            </div>
            <input class="submit-button" type="submit" value="Create">
          </form>
          <div class="create-cross" data-form="create"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="slider">
    <div class="slides">
      <img class="image image1" src="images/slide1.jpg" alt="image1">
      <img class="image image2" src="images/slide2.jpg" alt="image2">
      <img class="image image3" src="images/slide3.jpg" alt="image3">
    </div>
    <div class="sliderounds">
      <div class="slideround" data-image="1"></div>
      <div class="slideround" data-image="2"></div>
      <div class="slideround" data-image="3"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="title-text">
    Why our services ? 
  </div>
  <a>{{data.email}}</a>

  <a href="/userprofile/{{data.email}}" >{{data.email}}</a>
  <a href="/myproduct">  my product</a>
  <div class="text-box">
    <div class="title-box">
      <div class="text-round"></div>
      <p>Shopping</p>
    </div>
    <pre>Here you can find best quality product to buy.
There will be no any extra charge or margin for our services.
A product will have a same price for sellers and buyers.</pre>
  </div>

  <div class="text-box">
    <div class="title-box">
      <div class="text-round"></div>
      <p>Selling</p>
    </div>
    <pre>Here you sell your products to our best buyers and with best prices.
There will be no any extra charges or margin for our services.
A product will have a same price for sellers and buyers.
      </pre>
  </div>

  <div class="text-box">
    <div class="title-box">
      <div class="text-round"></div>
      <p>Deliver to earn</p>
    </div>
    <pre>It is our new feature.
With this feature you can earn some extra money while doing your daily travel.
Suppose, you want to go some place for your work and there is someone who want to
    send their product at same location where you want to go so now you can do their
    work without wasting too much time and buyer will give you money for delivery</pre>
  </div>
  <div class="text-box"></div>
  <div class="text-box"></div>
  <footer>
    {{> footer}}
  </footer>
  <script src="Java script/home.js"></script>
  <script src="Java script/javascript.js"></script>
</body>
</html>